1
00:00:05,175 --> 00:00:07,925
(Qiao Nian's home)

2
00:00:08,237 --> 00:00:09,240
(Qiao Nian, Qiao Group's heiress)

3
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:10,720
(Why am I in the courtyard?)

4
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:12,519
(Where's Jiang Zechen?)

5
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:27,519
(Jiang Zechen, Qiao Nian's husband)
(I... I'm in Zechen's body.)

6
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,559
- (Our consciousnesses have merged?)
- (Our consciousnesses have merged?)

7
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:33,000
=Fireworks=

8
00:00:33,137 --> 00:00:35,225
=Episode 1=

9
00:00:36,275 --> 00:00:38,662
(One day ago)

10
00:00:39,079 --> 00:00:41,960
Zechen, there's something important
at work tomorrow.

11
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:44,799
But tonight is about you and me only.

12
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:17,120
(I'm inheriting Qiao Group today.)

13
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:20,319
(I can finally have everything I want.)

14
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:24,920
I'm leaving.

15
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:31,200
What's wrong?

16
00:01:32,159 --> 00:01:33,159
Not satisfied?

17
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:34,599
I had dinner

18
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:36,200
but not breakfast yet.

19
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:47,840
I really have to go.

20
00:01:57,537 --> 00:01:58,337
Qiao Nian!

21
00:02:03,825 --> 00:02:05,987
(Which rascal dare touch Qiao Nian?)

22
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:08,439
(I won't let him off.)

23
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,479
(Lucheng, suburban reservoir)
Let me go!

24
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,719
Who sent you?

25
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:14,919
Was it my aunt?

26
00:02:15,090 --> 00:02:16,080
How much did she pay you?

27
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,400
I'll pay ten times that.

28
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,360
Apologies, Ms. Qiao.

29
00:02:19,479 --> 00:02:21,840
Credit is important
for our line of work.

30
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,879
Don't think you can get away
with killing me.

31
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,039
Listen to me.

32
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,520
The person who ordered you

33
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:29,560
won't let any witnesses live!

34
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:30,639
Are you done?

35
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,360
So slow.

36
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:35,360
Zechen!

37
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,039
Qiao Nian!

38
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:37,240
Zechen!

39
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:37,840
What the hell.

40
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:40,080
A tracker? You tricked me!

41
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:02,039
(Am I going to die just like this?)

42
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:10,560
(I once faced only endless darkness)

43
00:03:11,919 --> 00:03:13,439
(It wasn't until I was 18)

44
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:15,680
(that Grandpa brought me home.)

45
00:03:15,937 --> 00:03:16,375
(Qiao Residence)

46
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,960
- Welcome home, Ms. Qiao.
- Welcome home, Ms. Qiao.

47
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:22,280
Nian, we're home.

48
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,199
Okay.

49
00:03:26,879 --> 00:03:28,840
(I will take control of my life,)

50
00:03:29,575 --> 00:03:30,735
(find Mom,)

51
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:32,960
(and give her the best life.)

52
00:03:33,037 --> 00:03:38,820
♪Whose voice keeps climbing
into my dreams?♪

53
00:03:38,820 --> 00:03:42,580
♪I wake to quiet peace♪

54
00:03:43,337 --> 00:03:46,097
♪Time tells me to let go♪

55
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,919
(Zechen.)

56
00:03:50,380 --> 00:03:53,820
♪I waited through autumn leaves
and winter's decay♪

57
00:03:54,162 --> 00:03:56,660
♪Yet never got the chance♪

58
00:03:56,660 --> 00:04:01,660
♪To plant these blooming flowers
with you♪

59
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:04,520
(Qiao Nian, wake up. Don't sleep.)

60
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,759
(I know what you want to do.)

61
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,520
(I'll protect you)

62
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,360
(and beat all your enemies.)

63
00:04:23,887 --> 00:04:26,025
(Qiao Group, Lucheng)

64
00:04:27,212 --> 00:04:28,087
(Qiao Qibang, CEO of Qiao Group)

65
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:30,319
Qiao Nian's already late
on her first day.

66
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,600
I told you she can't be trusted.

67
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,319
This is ridiculous.

68
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,450
(Unknown number: Mission failed.)

69
00:04:37,450 --> 00:04:38,360
(Qiao Wenjun, Deputy CEO of Qiao Group)

70
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,560
(She is still alive?)

71
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:45,160
It's been over an hour,

72
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:46,360
but Qiao Nian isn't here yet.

73
00:04:46,759 --> 00:04:48,800
She clearly doesn't take us seriously.

74
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:51,959
I think the meeting can be dismissed.

75
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,637
(I will take back what's mine.)

76
00:04:59,839 --> 00:05:00,759
Hello, Ms. Qiao.

77
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:09,079
Nian, come to me.

78
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:09,759
Grandpa.

79
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:10,879
We were waiting for you.

80
00:05:12,199 --> 00:05:13,360
Apologies, everyone.

81
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,199
I got delayed on the way.

82
00:05:14,199 --> 00:05:15,560
- Hello, Ms. Qiao.
- Hi, Ms. Qiao.

83
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,360
I hereby announce

84
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:24,959
that starting today, Qiao Nian is
appointed CEO of Qiao Group.

85
00:05:34,199 --> 00:05:35,240
I object.

86
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,812
Qiao Nian lacks experience.

87
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:41,680
She's taking over the company
with just a few successful cases.

88
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:43,639
Any one of the shareholders here

89
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,879
have more experience than she has.

90
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:49,360
Who do you think has
the most experience?

91
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:51,590
Surely you don't mean yourself,
Aunt Wenjun?

92
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,439
There was a project last month

93
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,079
that caused us
tens of millions of losses.

94
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:58,639
That was your project, right?

95
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:01,839
(Duan Yiran, Qiao Nian's cousin)
Qiao Nian, watch your mouth!

96
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:03,800
Enough. Both of you.

97
00:06:03,962 --> 00:06:04,842
Miss Duan.

98
00:06:05,687 --> 00:06:06,350
(Bai Niansheng, secretary
of Qiao Group CEO)

99
00:06:06,387 --> 00:06:07,106
No.

100
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,680
I call the shots

101
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:14,800
on who inherits the company.

102
00:06:15,519 --> 00:06:16,399
Jiang Zechen.

103
00:06:24,439 --> 00:06:26,600
Mr. Qiao has no right
to appoint the next chairman.

104
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:28,720
All the projects in this file

105
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:32,800
were discovered by me
while working under him.

106
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:36,079
No wonder they were either halted

107
00:06:36,079 --> 00:06:37,519
or overtaken by competitors.

108
00:06:37,879 --> 00:06:39,879
So Mr. Qiao was responsible for them.

109
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,600
All these projects
caused severe losses to the group

110
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,279
due to Mr. Qiao's misjudgment.

111
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,600
These circulating funds

112
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,639
were handled solely by him

113
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,790
and transferred
into another mystery account.

114
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:54,160
(What's gotten into Zechen?)

115
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:56,000
Zechen,

116
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:58,759
you're Mr. Qiao's personal secretary.

117
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:03,319
What you're doing is clearly
a betrayal to the Qiao family.

118
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,040
Grandpa, are you alright?

119
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:07,839
I'm fine.

120
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:12,087
(This old man doesn't have
much time left anyways.)

121
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:17,439
Those in favor of removing Qiao Qibang
as chairman, please raise your hand.

122
00:07:21,759 --> 00:07:23,519
Majority wins.

123
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:25,959
Dad,

124
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:28,279
you lost.

125
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,920
(Because of money,)

126
00:07:30,399 --> 00:07:33,199
(even family can become enemies.)

127
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:35,137
Who said we lost?

128
00:07:38,439 --> 00:07:41,959
Those in favor of me as CEO,
please raise your hand.

129
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:44,079
- I agree.
- I agree.

130
00:07:44,850 --> 00:07:46,931
(What's going on with the shareholders?)

131
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,800
Wenjun,

132
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:53,519
Qiao Nian is the company's
largest shareholder now.

133
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,612
What?

134
00:07:55,879 --> 00:07:56,720
Jiang Zechen,

135
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,240
why didn't you tell me?

136
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:02,199
(Good thing I had a backup plan.)

137
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:10,399
So you two worked together
to trick me, huh?

138
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:11,959
Qiao Nian,

139
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:17,920
do you know if he married you
out of love?

140
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:24,800
Aunt Wenjun,

141
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:27,839
that's something I'll settle
with my husband privately.

142
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:29,319
You needn't worry.

143
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,319
By the way,

144
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:33,200
you haven't been yourself recently.

145
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:34,919
You should get some rest.

146
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,320
Meeting adjourned.

147
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:41,200
Grandpa, let's go.

148
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:44,879
(Wenjun, you've truly disappointed me.)

149
00:08:45,925 --> 00:08:48,525
Mom, Qiao Nian has gone too far.

150
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:52,960
(Girl, I'll deal with you soon.)

151
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,200
Jiang Zechen,

152
00:08:58,559 --> 00:09:00,480
send my regards to your dad.

153
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,240
Nian.

154
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:06,399
Hmm?

155
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,639
Before loving someone else,

156
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:11,960
you must remember to love yourself.

157
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,159
Alright?

158
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:19,759
Nian.

159
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:20,360
Yeah?

160
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:24,240
Once you're in charge,
you won't be as free anymore.

161
00:09:24,799 --> 00:09:26,879
Remember to visit me often.

162
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,759
Mmm.

163
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:30,240
Every time we see each other

164
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:33,399
is one less time we'll meet again.

165
00:09:33,559 --> 00:09:35,320
Oh, Grandpa. What are you saying?

166
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:37,840
You'll live a long life.

167
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:40,200
Just like Laifu here.

168
00:09:41,559 --> 00:09:43,000
Alright.

169
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:44,720
You're right.

170
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,320
Okay.

171
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,075
- Hmm.
- Okay.

172
00:09:46,075 --> 00:09:46,876
We're leaving.

173
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,639
Drive safe.

174
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:49,080
Goodbye.

175
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:49,759
Bye, Grandpa.

176
00:09:49,759 --> 00:09:50,960
Come visit me soon.

177
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,759
Bye-bye.

178
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,159
Hurry back in.

179
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,320
Bye-bye, Grandpa.

180
00:09:58,639 --> 00:10:00,480
(She must hate me in her heart.)

181
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:02,360
Qiao Nian!

182
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,159
The plan you used
to defeat Qiao Wenjun at the meeting

183
00:10:10,639 --> 00:10:13,080
was because you knew
who I was, wasn't it?

184
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:15,440
Jiang Zechen,

185
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,639
I only have one question.

186
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:19,120
Was our marriage

187
00:10:20,919 --> 00:10:24,440
because of true love
or a carefully planned scheme?

188
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,240
Let's get divorced.

189
00:10:27,639 --> 00:10:28,279
Qiao Nian.

190
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,039
I won't let go.

191
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,279
You must've foreseen

192
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:41,799
that things would end up like this.

193
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:46,480
I really

194
00:10:47,399 --> 00:10:48,879
truly don't want to see you again.

195
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,600
(Qiao Nian,)

196
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,240
(I had no choice.)

197
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,039
(Jiang Residence, Lucheng)
I'll kill you!

198
00:10:59,881 --> 00:11:01,200
You just had to butt in.

199
00:11:01,287 --> 00:11:02,527
Wanted to play the hero, huh?

200
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,200
I'll kill you!

201
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:11,639
(Jiang Xiao, CEO of Jiang Group)
Qiao Wenjun wanted to remove Qiao Nian.

202
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:14,360
Why did you butt in and save her?

203
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,039
Qiao Nian...

204
00:11:18,279 --> 00:11:19,399
is my wife.

205
00:11:20,519 --> 00:11:24,039
If she inherits the company,

206
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:29,075
I can't guarantee
if your brother will still be alive.

207
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,600
(Due to the geomagnetic storm,)

208
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:32,639
(some areas of the city)

209
00:11:32,639 --> 00:11:35,879
(will experience unusual
thunderstorm tonight.)

210
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,919
(Citizens are advised
to take precautions.)

211
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,039
Grandpa,

212
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,720
don't worry.

213
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:48,360
I won't let anyone
who harms the company off.

214
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:01,879
(And you're first,)

215
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:03,759
(Divorce Agreement)
(Jiang Zechen.)

216
00:12:12,887 --> 00:12:15,762
♪The sky's waiting for the fog to clear♪

217
00:12:16,775 --> 00:12:19,775
♪Like ears waiting for an answer♪

218
00:12:19,850 --> 00:12:20,637
(Divorce Agreement)

219
00:12:20,637 --> 00:12:26,237
♪Those lost still struggle on♪

220
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,399
(It's all not real,)

221
00:12:29,399 --> 00:12:30,279
(Jiang Zechen.)

222
00:12:32,300 --> 00:12:35,580
♪Love never carved its way to the end♪

223
00:12:36,180 --> 00:12:41,900
♪Yet I still look at you at the end♪

224
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:49,320
♪Whose voice keeps climbing
into my dreams?♪

225
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,120
(Qiao Nian,)

226
00:12:52,039 --> 00:12:53,759
(will you forgive me?)

227
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:57,860
♪Time tells me to let go♪

228
00:12:57,860 --> 00:13:01,580
♪I waited through spring rain
and summer’s fading heat♪

229
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:04,559
(Such a beautiful firework,)

230
00:13:05,519 --> 00:13:07,720
(but not a single one belongs to me.)

231
00:13:08,460 --> 00:13:12,820
♪To plant these blooming flowers
with you♪

232
00:13:12,879 --> 00:13:13,679
Hello.

233
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:16,039
You have a parcel at management
that hasn't been picked up.

234
00:13:16,039 --> 00:13:17,240
I've placed it at your door.

235
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,300
Coming.

236
00:13:27,639 --> 00:13:28,437
(Where is he?)

237
00:13:31,587 --> 00:13:32,548
(Qiao Nian!)

238
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:37,720
Let go of me!

239
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:38,799
Stop struggling!

240
00:13:42,650 --> 00:13:43,451
Stop there!

241
00:13:44,362 --> 00:13:45,161
Stop!

242
00:13:46,875 --> 00:13:47,915
You have nowhere to run.

243
00:13:50,537 --> 00:13:51,338
Don't come closer!

244
00:13:52,375 --> 00:13:53,735
What do you want?

245
00:13:53,735 --> 00:13:55,153
It's always these cheap tricks!

246
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,279
When will this end?

247
00:14:00,919 --> 00:14:03,679
You're an illegitimate child
but want to inherit the company.

248
00:14:04,039 --> 00:14:05,240
Go die!

249
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:08,240
(I won't let you get your way.)

250
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:15,559
Qiao Nian!

251
00:14:30,159 --> 00:14:30,960
Don't be scared.

252
00:14:37,039 --> 00:14:37,919
Let her go!

253
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,840
(You saved me again and again.)

254
00:14:40,799 --> 00:14:42,879
(But why did you betray me?)

255
00:14:46,725 --> 00:14:47,524
Darn it.

256
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,890
(I'll take Qiao Nian away first.)

257
00:14:54,110 --> 00:14:55,590
(You won't be inheriting the company.)

258
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,639
My body!

259
00:15:07,799 --> 00:15:09,240
What's happening?

260
00:15:12,799 --> 00:15:13,679
Qiao Nian.

261
00:15:14,325 --> 00:15:15,965
Thank god you're okay.

262
00:15:16,679 --> 00:15:17,480
Qiao Nian.

263
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:18,799
Zechen.

264
00:15:44,337 --> 00:15:50,300
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

265
00:15:50,580 --> 00:15:58,187
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

266
00:15:58,237 --> 00:16:02,020
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

267
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:05,820
♪Where this ends♪

268
00:16:05,820 --> 00:16:13,100
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

269
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:17,437
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

270
00:16:17,475 --> 00:16:20,555
♪Love turns into pain♪

271
00:16:20,625 --> 00:16:24,745
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

272
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:28,387
♪Yet I still want you close♪

273
00:16:28,387 --> 00:16:32,550
